articles.title: Dengue, Mosquito-Borne Diseases Rising In Europe Due To Climate Change - NDTV
articles.description: Cases of dengue and other mosquito-borne diseases are rising significantly in Europe as climate change creates warmer conditions that help invasive mosquitos spread, the EU's health agency warned on Tuesday.
